definition.value: An N-acyl-D-glucosamine 1-phosphate in which the phosphate group of 2-(acetylamino)-2-deoxyglucose 1-phosphate is esterified by the alcoholic hydroxy group of L-serine.
A diterpene produced by a bacterial diterpene synthase from Allokutzneria albata.
